comment: Permissions used by the AdServices APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_TOPICS
variables.comment: This permission needs to be declared by the caller of Topics APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_ATTRIBUTION
variables.comment: This permission needs to be declared by the caller of Attribution APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_CUSTOM_AUDIENCE
variables.comment: This permission needs to be declared by the caller of Custom Audiences APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_PROTECTED_SIGNALS
variables.comment: This permission needs to be declared by the caller of Protected Signals APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_AD_SELECTION
variables.comment: This permission needs to be declared by the caller of Protected Signals APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_AD_ID
variables.comment: This permission needs to be declared by the caller of Advertising ID APIs.

variables.name: ACCESS_PRIVILEGED_AD_ID
variables.comment:
* This is a signature permission that needs to be declared by the AdServices apk to access API
     * for AdID provided by another provider service. The signature permission is required to make
     * sure that only AdServices is permitted to access this api.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: ACCESS_PRIVILEGED_APP_SET_ID
variables.comment:
* This is a signature permission needs to be declared by the AdServices apk to access API for
     * AppSetId provided by another provider service. The signature permission is required to make
     * sure that only AdServices is permitted to access this api.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: MODIFY_ADSERVICES_STATE
variables.comment:
* The permission that lets it modify AdService's enablement state modification API.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: MODIFY_ADSERVICES_STATE_COMPAT
variables.comment:
* The permission that lets it modify AdService's enablement state modification API on S-.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_STATE
variables.comment:
* The permission that lets it access AdService's enablement state modification API.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_STATE_COMPAT
variables.comment:
* The permission that lets it access AdService's enablement state modification API on S-.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: ACCESS_ADSERVICES_MANAGER
variables.comment:
* The permission needed to call AdServicesManager APIs
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: ACCESS_PRIVILEGED_ADSERVICES_COBALT_UPLOAD
variables.comment:
* This is a signature permission needs to be declared by the AdServices apk to access API for
     * AdServices Cobalt upload service provided by another provider service. The signature
     * permission is required to make sure that only AdServices is permitted to access this api.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: UPDATE_PRIVILEGED_AD_ID
variables.comment:
* The permission that allows calling updating AdId Cache API via Common Service.
     *
     * @hide

variables.name: UPDATE_PRIVILEGED_AD_ID_COMPAT
variables.comment:
* The permission that allows calling updating AdId Cache API via Common Service on S-.
     *
     * @hide
